1. Add the mock service to the `index.ts` file in the services directory

    src/services/index.ts
    ```typescript
    ...
    export * from './stock-items-mock.service';
    ```

1. Start the service

    ```bash
   npm start
    ```

1. Open a browser to `http://localhost:3000/api-docs` and execute the stock items controller

