1. Update the title and subtitle with values for our Stock Items view. The `formatters` entry can be
set to `{}` as well.

    components/StockItemList.jsx
    ```javascript
    class StockItemList extends Component {
      title = 'Stock Items';
      subtitle = 'This is the current inventory of items';
      formatters = {};

      ...
    }
    ```

1. The result of these changes should look like the following:

    components/StockItemList.jsx
    ```javascript
    class StockItemList extends Component {
        title = 'Stock Items';
        subtitle = 'This is the current inventory of items';

        columns = [
        "name",
