    ```

   replacing `{your initials}` with your actual initials

1. Open the [pipeline to see it running](/getting-started/deploy-app#view-your-application-pipeline)

1. When the pipeline is completed, run `igc ingress -n dev-{your initials}`. You should see an entry
for the app we just pushed. Select the entry and hit `Enter` to launch the browser.

